# Planning Rules

This is the Cursor adapter for Hecate planning guidance.

The canonical planning rules live in
[`docs-ai/core/workflow.md`](../../docs-ai/core/workflow.md) and the plan
template lives in [`docs-ai/tasks/planning.md`](../../docs-ai/tasks/planning.md).
Use [`docs-ai/skills/architect/SKILL.md`](../../docs-ai/skills/architect/SKILL.md)
for substantial changes that need a plan before code.

Do not copy planning triggers or wire-field checklists into Cursor rules. Link
to the canonical docs instead.

Provider wire-field changes use the canonical chain in
[`docs-ai/skills/providers/SKILL.md`](../../docs-ai/skills/providers/SKILL.md).
